templates.name: objets by ids $liste ( (prefLabelFr séparées par des virgules) PAIHABIT0000000007540173,CONSPONC0000000353861389
templates.cypher:
match (o:ObjetGeo) where o.id in  split($liste,",")
return o

templates.name: name equals $string
templates.cypher: match (o:ObjetGeo) where toLower(o.name) = toLower($string) return o;

templates.name: name contains $string
templates.cypher: match (o:ObjetGeo) where toLower(o.name) contains toLower($string) return o;

templates.name: commune de $name
templates.cypher:
match (o:ObjetGeo {name:$name})-[:hasGeometry]->(g:geom)
 with g.WKTGeometryEncoder as geom ,o
call spatial.intersects("polygons",geom) yield node 
with o,node match (node)-[:hasGeometry]-(c:Commune)
return c,o
